# AI Logic Agent

Server simulates; client renders NPCs and enemies.

- NPCs: `ProfessionAiManager.tick()` in `GameRoom.simulateTick()`.
- Behaviors: `professionBehaviors.ts`, `BaseProfessionBehavior.ts` (move-to-target).
- Enemies: biome-weighted spawn via `ENEMY_SPAWN_DEFINITIONS`; combat not yet implemented.
- Mutate `WorldState.npcs` / `enemies` only on server; client reads from sync.
